window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>New town. New school. Same nightmare.</b></p> <p>When I lost my mom, I thought the worst was over. Moving to Sun Valley to live with a father I barely know is punishment all over again.</p> <p>I need to survive the year, then leave this town behind.</p> <p>Roman Valdez has other plans. Star receiver. King of the school. The Devil in cleats. From day one, it's his mission to ruin me.</p> <p>Except something about his actions doesn't add up. One moment, he's tearing me apart. The next, he's stepping in, protecting me like I belong to him.</p> <p>His touch burns, his words cut, and every glance pulls me deeper into a dangerous game I can't afford to lose.</p> <p>In a town where football is everything, Roman Valdez might be the one thing that breaks me—or the only one who can make me whole.</p>"; 
